'''Sah'c Canyon''' was located in the [[Quadrant H-46|Sah'c District]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was lined by skyscrapers and a [[Hovertrain/Legends|mag-lev train]] rail, and led to the [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Chancellor's]] emergency command bunker from the [[Senate District/Legends|Senate District]]. It was used as the escape route for the Supreme Chancellor [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] during the [[Battle of Coruscant/Legends|Battle of Coruscant]].

